Privacy Policy - HuskyDEV Watch Faces
HuskyDEV (“us”, “we”, or “our”) is a developer of all the HuskyDEV Watch Faces on the Google Play store (
link to all watch faces
) - mobile applications (hereinafter referred to as the “Application”).
Information Collection and Use
Your privacy is very important to us. So check what we do:
We don’t ask you for any personal information
We don’t share/sell your personal information with anyone.
We don’t store your personal information.
We don’t transfer any personal information from your mobile or watch
The Application does use third-party services that may collect information used to identify you.
Link to the privacy policy of third-party service providers used by the app
